                     <author key="person_67528596">Pietro da Lucca (Petrus Lucensis)</author>
                     <title key="work_3682">theological works</title>
                     <note>A transcript of 'Opusculo de trenta documenti per persone... spirituale. 
                        Et doctrina del ben morire con molte utile resolutione de alcuni belli dubii Teologici' 
                        that was copied from the edition printed at Bologna by Hieronymus de Benedictis on 20 June 1518 (see p. cxxxvii)</note>
                     <note>On pp. cxxxviii-cliv is 'Opera noua chiamata Luce di fede...'</note>
                     <note>There are also small theological lists and pieces that may be derived from the printed volume</note>
                     <note>Pietro da Lucca's name is in the dedications</note>
